CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1783680590
OL,3,CAmber heat health alert issued for
OL,4,CSouth West
OL,6,FThe South West has been placed under
OL,7,Fan amber heat health alert from today
OL,8,F(8 July), warning that there's a
OL,9,Fgreater risk to life for vulnerable
OL,10,Fpeople.
OL,12,FThe alert from the UK Health Security
OL,13,FAgency (UKHSA) comes into force at 9am
OL,14,FBST as temperatures are expected to
OL,15,Freach thirty degrees across the region
OL,16,Fthis week. The alert ends on Sunday
OL,17,F(12 July) at 9pm BST.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
