OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,405,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1783680590
OL,3,CAmber heat health alert issued for
OL,4,CSouth West
OL,6,FThe UKHSA issue these alerts when
OL,7,Fthere's going to be a period of
OL,8,Fprolonged hot weather that's very
OL,9,Flikely to impact people and services.
OL,11,FEmily Moseley, from UKHSA South West,
OL,12,Ftold ITV News: "These weather alerts
OL,13,Freally help us to look ahead and to
OL,14,Fhelp our system prepare for any impact
OL,15,Fit could have on our health and
OL,16,Finfrastructure."
OL,26,@tD@POU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,405,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1783680590
OL,3,CAmber heat health alert issued for
OL,4,CSouth West
OL,6,FMs Moseley warns that the people who
OL,7,Fare most vulnerable during the hot
OL,8,Fweather are older people, children,
OL,9,Fpregnant women and those in vulnerable
OL,10,Fcategories.
OL,12,F"If you know your elderly neighbour
OL,13,Flives by themselves, it's important to
OL,14,Fcheck in and make sure they're doing
OL,15,Feverything they can to stay cool and
OL,16,Fsupport them in any way you can."
OL,18,FThe UKHSA says health and social care
OL,19,Fservices are likely to experience
OL,20,Fincreased demand during the high
OL,21,Ftemperatures.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,405,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1783680590
OL,3,CAmber heat health alert issued for
OL,4,CSouth West
OL,6,FThe government body also says water-
OL,7,Frelated incidents could increase, such
OL,8,Fas cold water shock from those
OL,9,Fentering the water to stay cool.
OL,11,FWith people likely to be out in the
OL,12,Fsun during the high temperatures at
OL,13,Fthe weekend, the UKHSA has advised
OL,14,Fthose drinking alcohol to keep
OL,15,Fhydrated by drinking water and keeping
OL,16,Fcool as much as possible.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,405,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1783680590
OL,3,CAmber heat health alert issued for
OL,4,CSouth West
OL,6,FIt follows the South Western Ambulance
OL,7,FService NHS Foundation Trust (SWASFT)
OL,8,Fexperiencing its busiest day on record
OL,9,Flast month (25 June) when the region
OL,10,Fwas placed under a red heat health
OL,11,Falert, with the demand partly driven
OL,12,Fby people reporting heat-related
OL,13,Fhealth incidents, such as sunstroke,
OL,14,Fdehydration and sunburn.
OL,16,FAnalysis from West Country's Weather
OL,17,FPresenter, Charlie Powell
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,405,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1783680590
OL,3,CAmber heat health alert issued for
OL,4,CSouth West
OL,6,F"A third heatwave in as many months,
OL,7,Fbut this one will feel a bit different
OL,8,Fto June's although it'll still be hot
OL,9,Fwith temperatures expected to reach
OL,10,Fthe low-to-mid thirties. The area of
OL,11,Fhigh pressure delivering the settled
OL,12,Fweather is to the southwest of the UK,
OL,13,Fwhich means the air is circulating
OL,14,Fover the Atlantic and not mainland
OL,15,FEurope. Humidity therefore won't be as
OL,16,Fhigh and it should be slightly more
OL,17,Fmanageable heat as a result.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,405,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1783680590
OL,3,CAmber heat health alert issued for
OL,4,CSouth West
OL,6,F"The main question this time around is
OL,7,Fhow long the above average
OL,8,Ftemperatures will last as there
OL,9,Fdoesn't appear to be a quick change
OL,10,Flike we saw at the end of June.
OL,11,FCurrent forecasts show a steady
OL,12,Fdecline to more normal temperatures
OL,13,F(around 21 C in July for the West
OL,14,FCountry) in a couple of weeks time.
OL,26,@uD@LOX
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,405,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1783680590
OL,3,CAmber heat health alert issued for
OL,4,CSouth West
OL,6,F"Does that mean we'll have another
OL,7,Fextreme heat warning from the Met
OL,8,FOffice? Not necessarily - the fact
OL,9,Fthat the heat is more manageable and
OL,10,Fless extreme, even if it lasts a
OL,11,Fwhile, means there should be less
OL,12,Fimpact (the basis of Met Office
OL,13,FNational Severe Weather Warnings) on
OL,14,Finfrastructure and day-to-day life.
OL,15,FThere's more time to adjust to the
OL,16,Fheat as it builds and subsides at a
OL,17,Fslower pace.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,405,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40409
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1783680590
OL,3,CAmber heat health alert issued for
OL,4,CSouth West
OL,6,F"However, the UKHSA has issued an
OL,7,Famber alert which is "intended to
OL,8,Fprovide early warning to the health
OL,9,Fand social care sector, the responder
OL,10,Fcommunity, the voluntary and community
OL,11,Fsector and government departments when
OL,12,Fadverse temperatures are likely to
OL,13,Fimpact on the health and wellbeing of
OL,14,Fthe population."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
